data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Tampa/Carrollwood! This modern and stylish 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom townhouse boasts a spacious rooftop space and a deck, perfect for relaxing and entertaining with family and friends. As you step into this beautifully designed townhouse, you'll immediately notice the elegant concrete flooring of the home. The laundry closet is conveniently located upstairs for easy access. The master bedroom upstairs features a spacious walk-in closet and an ensuite bath complete with his and her sinks, toilet, and walk-in shower, perfect for unwinding after a long day. One bedroom downstairs also has its own ensuite bath, making it ideal for accommodating guests or family members. The kitchen features solid wood cabinets, ample storage, granite counters, and a breakfast bar. The living room is the perfect space to relax and unwind, with a beautiful view of the lake and quick access to the deck. This gated community provides two assigned parking spots in front of the unit for your convenience. You'll enjoy breathtaking lake views from the comfort of your own home. Built in 2019, this property is in pristine condition and ready for you to move in! The HOA fee includes access to the community pool, maintenance of the exterior, grounds, repairs, and trash. Located just off Dale Mabry Highway and the Veterans Express Highway, this property offers easy access to Tampa International Airport, Raymond James Stadium, and the International Mall. You'll love the convenience of living in the heart of Tampa/Carrollwood while still enjoying the peace and tranquility of this beautiful townhouse. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to make this stunning property your own!
